      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET GODDESS (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 8 last run (27.73) at this track. Is yet to taste defeat in two starts from this draw. Leading chance again. SUNSET CALIGULA (3) was well supported last time and rocketed out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but had to settle for the minor money, finishing a half a length second (27.53) over 488m at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Hard to beat again. TIC TAC MONELLI (2) pinged the lids last start from an awkward draw and led throughout to score (27.50) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 488m. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Has definite claims. NERA CARNEY (4) is a chance after winning last time.",
